> 01:19:51,520\nWas he gonna report it?\n\n892\n01:19:51,979 --> 01:19:53,979\nGet his daughter arrested?\n\n893\n01:19:58,229 --> 01:20:00,146\nHe did something better than that\n\n894\n01:20:00,729 --> 01:20:03,354\nHe waited until he found\nout where I wound up\n\n895\n01:20:03,646 --> 01:20:04,729\nOne morning\n\n896\n01:20:04,938 --> 01:20:07,396\na FedEx guy comes with an envelope for me\n\n897\n01:20:07,604 --> 01:20:10,563\nInside the envelope''s the title\nand registration of the car\n\n898\n01:20:14,896 --> 01:20:17,354\nSon of a bitch signed it over to me\n\n899\n01:20:20,313 --> 01:20:21,396\nSo\n\n900\n01:20:22,146 --> 01:20:24,979\nI''m gonna drive this car until it falls apart\n\n901\n01:20:25,271 --> 01:20:26,604\nAt least until I do\n\n902\n01:20:32,479 --> 01:20:34,438\nSo what am I supposed to?\n\n903\n01:20:35,688 --> 01:20:38,188\nWell, Beth\n\n904\n01:20:39,354 --> 01:20:42,521\nI told you I lost everything back at Harlan''s,\ndidn''t I?\n\n905\n01:20:42,771 --> 01:20:43,771\nYeah\n\n906\n01:20:44,021 --> 01:20:47,104\nWell, that''s not exactly how it went down\n\n907\n01:20:48,354 --> 01:20:51,438\nSee, I beat that game on its ass, Beth\n\n908\n01:20:52,479 --> 01:20:54,813\nI knocked them off their feet\n\n909\n01:20:55,854 --> 01:20:58,563\nThe cards turned just like I knew they would\n\n910\n01:20:58,854 --> 01:21:01,021\nI read the other players just right\n\n911\n01:21:04,063 --> 01:21:06,104\nI walked away with all their money\n\n912\n01:21:06,604 --> 01:21:07,854\nSo you lied to me\n\n913\n01:21:10,271 --> 01:21:12,063\nMaybe I didn''t want to share\n\n914\n01:21:12,646 --> 01:21:16,021\nMaybe I just wanted to see how trusting\nand gullible you were\n\n915\n01:21:18,229 --> 01:21:21,229\nMaybe I just wanted company. You know?\n\n916\n01:21:21,521 --> 01:21:23,188\nIt''s a long ride, Beth\n\n917\n01:21:25,063 --> 01:21:26,813\nI didn''t want to go alone\n\n918\n01:22:06,021 --> 01:22:08,188\nCan''t do it.\nThirty-five hundred''s the best I can give ya\n\n919\n01:22:08,229 --> 01:22:10,438\nThree thousand. That''s my top\n\n920\n01:22:10,729 --> 01:22:13,063\nCan''t. Gotta have thirty-five hundred. Sorry\n\n921\n01:22:13,270 --> 01:22:14,951\nThirty-two hundred. Take it or leave it\n\n922\n01:22:15,104 --> 01:22:15,729\nYou know what?\n\n923\n01:22:15,979 --> 01:22:18,563\nI''m sure we can find a better deal\nsomeplace else. Let''s go\n\n924\n01:22:18,896 --> 01:22:20,938\nI don''t think you will, ladies.\nSuit yourselves\n\n925\n01:22:21,146 --> 01:22:22,104\nThank you!\n\n926\n01:22:24,063 --> 01:22:25,021\nDon''t look back\n\n927\n01:22:25,396 --> 01:22:26,271\nBeth, where are you going?\n\n928\n01:22:26,521 --> 01:22:27,354\nI want that car\n\n929\n01:22:27,521 --> 01:22:28,479\nBeth not at that price!\n\n930\n01:22:28,854 --> 01:22:31,396\nWe can get it for three grand by the time\nwe get to my car\n\n931\n01:22:32,229 --> 01:22:33,938\nI don''t think he''s gonna come down\n\n932\n01:22:34,188 --> 01:22:36,271\nAnd I think that''s the car I want\n\n933\n01:22:37,354 --> 01:22:40,354\nHave you learned nothing\nfrom your time with me?\n\n934\n01:22:40,896 --> 01:22:43,396\nYou have to stop taking people at their word!\n\n935\n01:22:44,313 --> 01:22:45,729\nMaybe you should start\n\n936\n01:22:48,479 --> 01:22:49,896\nYou''re hopeless\n\n937\n01:22:51,104 --> 01:22:52,271\nYou''re hopeless too\n\n938\n01:23:09,063 --> 01:23:10,354\nDear Jeremy\n\n939\n01:23:10,938 --> 01:23:14,604\nIn the last few days,\nI''ve been learning how to not trust people\n\n940\n01:23:15,104 --> 01:23:16,688\nand I''m glad I failed\n\n941\n01:23:26,771 --> 01:23:29,771\nSometimes we depend on other people\nas a mirror\n\n942\n01:23:30,063 --> 01:23:32,771\nTo define us and tell us who we are\n\n943\n01:23:34,521 --> 01:23:37,771\nAnd each reflection makes me\nlike myself a little more\n\n944\n01:23:39,188 --> 01:23:40,646\nElizabeth\n\n945\n01:24:06,271 --> 01:24:07,646\nHello, Cafe Klyuch\n\n946\n01:24:47,688 --> 01:24:50,188\nRent\n\n947\n01:25:35,646 --> 01:25:36,896\nYou still open?\n\n948\n01:25:37,646 --> 01:25:39,979\nNo reason for me to still be here if I wasn''t\n\n949\n01:25:41,854 --> 01:25:44,521\nI heard this place has the best coffee\nand pie in town\n\n950\n01:25:44,771 --> 01:25:45,688\nWhere''d you hear that?\n\n951\n01:25:46,813 --> 01:25:48,146\nI get around\n\n952\n01:25:51,646 --> 01:25:52,854\nYou wanna come inside?\n\n953\n01:25:54,563 --> 01:25:55,479\nIt''s cold\n\n954\n01:25:56,021 --> 01:25:57,771\nWhat are you doing out here? It''s freezing\n\n955\n01:25:58,021 --> 01:26:00,313\nIt''s a beautiful night.\nI wanted to get some fresh air\n\n956\n01:26:01,813 --> 01:26:02,938\nHave a seat\n\n957\n01:26:07,813 --> 01:26:09,229\nIsn''t this reserved?\n\n958\n01:26:10,021 --> 01:26:11,146\nReserved for you\n\n959\n01:26:17,354 --> 01:26:18,646\nWant something to eat?\n\n960\n01:26:21,021 --> 01:26:23,104\nYeah, I''m starving\n\n961\n01:26:24,354 --> 01:26:25,646\nWhat''s good tonight?\n\n962\n01:26:26,729 --> 01:26:28,479\nWhat about a steak?\n\n963\n01:26:29,521 --> 01:26:30,729\nThat sounds good\n\n964\n01:26:32,021 --> 01:26:33,229\nDoes it come with home fries?\n\n965\n01:26:33,229 --> 01:26:34,271\nOr mashed\n\n966\n01:26:34,563 --> 01:26:35,729\nThey both sound good\n\n967\n01:26:36,271 --> 01:26:37,604\nHalf an order of both?\n\n968\n01:26:39,271 --> 01:26:41,688\nI''ll get the home fries with the steak,\nmedium rare\n\n969\n01:26:41,938 --> 01:26:44,021\nand a side of mashed potatoes\n\n970\n01:26:44,396 --> 01:26:45,563\nComing right up\n\n971\n01:26:58,146 --> 01:26:59,813\nLearning something about me?\n\n972\n01:27:01,729 --> 01:27:03,563\nThere''s something different about you\n\n973\n01:27:03,979 --> 01:27:05,604\nOr maybe it''s me that''s changed\n\n974\n01:27:08,438 --> 01:27:09,854\nWhere are the keys?\n\n975\n01:27:10,063 --> 01:27:11,396\nYou don''t keep them anymore?\n\n976\n01:27:13,271 --> 01:27:15,396\nBeen trying to give them\nback to their owners\n\n977\n01:27:15,771 --> 01:27:16,813\nDo you want yours?\n\n978\n01:27:17,021 --> 01:27:19,688\nNo. I don''t need them anymore\n\n979\n01:27:22,521 --> 01:27:23,813\nWhat about your keys?\n\n980\n01:27:26,354 --> 01:27:27,563\nI got rid of them\n\n981\n01:27:30,938 --> 01:27:31,938\nGood night, Jeremy\n\n982\n01:27:32,188 --> 01:27:33,354\nI''ll see you tomorrow\n\n983\n01:27:48,229 --> 01:27:50,354\nYou know I came here the night I left\n\n984\n01:27:51,063 --> 01:27:53,188\nbut I didn''t make it past the front door\n\n985\n01:27:57,063 --> 01:28:00,146\nI almost walked in but I knew that if I did\n\n986\n01:28:00,438 --> 01:28:03,188\nI would just be the same old Elizabeth\n\n987\n01:28:04,604 --> 01:28:06,604\nI didn''t want to be that person anymore\n\n988\n01:28:21,438 --> 01:28:22,646\nHope you enjoy it\n\n989\n01:28:32,729 --> 01:28:35,063\nAre they still left untouched at the end\nof the night?\n\n990\n01:28:35,354 --> 01:28:37,104\nYep, more or less\n\n991\n01:28:39,146 --> 01:28:41,188\nThen why do you keep making them?\n\n992\n01:28:44,938 --> 01:28:47,229\nWell I always like having one around\njust in case\n\n993\n01:28:47,688 --> 01:28:50,271\nyou pop in and fancy a slice\n\n994\n01:28:55,688 --> 01:28:58,021\nDo you remember that last night\nyou were here?\n\n995\n01:28:59,938 --> 01:29:02,396\nWhen you practically ate an entire pie\nall by yourself?\n\n996\n01:29:03,646 --> 01:29:04,688\nReally?\n\n997\n01:29:06,646 --> 01:29:09,396\nI remember getting really drunk and\n\n998\n01:29:09,479 --> 01:29:12,229\nhaving a god awful hangover the next day\n\n999\n01:29:13,146 --> 01:29:14,354\nNothing else?\n\n1000\n01:29:17,021 --> 01:29:19,438\nNo, nothing else\n\n1001\n01:29:24,771 --> 01:29:26,979\nOr don''t you have a tape I can watch?\n\n1002\n01:29:28,813 --> 01:29:30,729\nI do... but...\n\n1003\n01:29:31,479 --> 01:29:33,021\nI''ve watched it so many times\n\n1004\n01:29:33,270 --> 01:29:35,333\nthat the picture started fading\nto black and white\n\n1005\n01:29:35,354 --> 01:29:37,688\nAnd now it''s completely unwatchable\n\n1006\n01:29:37,850 --> 01:29:39,297\nMust have been an interesting night\n\n1007\n01:29:39,333 --> 01:29:40,020\nIt was\n\n1008\n01:29:46,438 --> 01:29:48,813\nNever seen a girl eat so much in all my life\n\n1009\n01:29:51,979 --> 01:29:53,104\nLike this?\n\n1010\n01:29:56,563 --> 01:29:58,063\nNo, it was more like this\n\n1011\n01:30:06,354 --> 01:30:07,771\nIt''s good pie\n\n1012\n01:31:35,479 --> 01:31:38,229\nIt took me nearly a year to get here\n\n1013\n01:31:40,604 --> 01:31:43,563\nIt wasn''t so hard to\ncross that street after all\n\n1014\n01:31:45,063 --> 01:31:48,313\nIt all depends on who''s waiting for you\non the other side\n\n');
