ons\nto feed the poor--\n\n162\n00:13:47,556 --> 00:13:51,519\n[ Whispering ]\nHowie. Go on.\nTalk to him.\n\n163\n00:13:51,602 --> 00:13:54,522\nGo on.\n\n164\n00:13:54,605 --> 00:13:57,817\nYou''re really from...\nup there?\n\n165\n00:13:59,109 --> 00:14:01,028\nIndeed.\n\n166\n00:14:02,488 --> 00:14:04,990\nI am from K-PAX.\n\n167\n00:14:05,074 --> 00:14:07,660\nWhat--\n\n168\n00:14:07,785 --> 00:14:10,329\nWhat sort of place is it?\n\n169\n00:14:10,412 --> 00:14:13,165\nK-PAX is bigger\nthan your planet.\n\n170\n00:14:13,249 --> 00:14:18,295\nBut we are circled\nby seven purple moons.\n\n171\n00:14:18,379 --> 00:14:21,006\nBullshit, bullshit,\nbullshit, bullshit,\n\n172\n00:14:21,090 --> 00:14:23,884\nbullshit, bullshit,\nbullshit.\n\n173\n00:14:23,968 --> 00:14:25,553\nGo on.\n\n174\n00:14:29,014 --> 00:14:33,519\nWell, K-PAX is most lovely\nwhen K-MON and K-RIL\nare in conjunction.\n\n175\n00:14:33,644 --> 00:14:38,190\nThose are our two suns.\nWhat you would call\nAgape and Satori.\n\n176\n00:14:44,530 --> 00:14:46,407\n[ Train Clacking ]\n\n177\n00:15:00,421 --> 00:15:02,298\n[ Car Door Slams ]\n\n178\n00:15:08,137 --> 00:15:12,057\nYou finish\nYour homework, Abby?\nYeah.\n\n179\n00:15:12,141 --> 00:15:14,143\nI lost another tooth.\n\n180\n00:15:14,268 --> 00:15:18,063\nOh, yeah? Let me see.\nHey! Maybe the tooth fairy\nwill come tonight, huh?\n\n181\n00:15:18,147 --> 00:15:20,316\nThere''s no such thing\nas the tooth fairy, Dad.\n\n182\n00:15:20,441 --> 00:15:22,818\nThere’s just you and Mom.\n\n183\n00:15:22,943 --> 00:15:26,947\nI fed them already.\nI couldn''t wait.\nHow was your day?\n\n184\n00:15:27,072 --> 00:15:31,452\nOh, 6:15 was late.\nDidn''t leave the station\ntil 6.:30.\n\n185\n00:15:31,535 --> 00:15:33,454\nShould have caught\nthe nearest beam of light.\n\n186\n00:15:33,537 --> 00:15:35,456\nYou should have caught what?\n\n187\n00:15:35,539 --> 00:15:38,083\nOh, nothing.\nHow was your day?\nGood.\n\n188\n00:15:38,167 --> 00:15:42,046\nSent the