n K-PAX.\n\n335\n00:25:33,386 --> 00:25:35,722\nThere are no wives.\nThere are no husbands.\n\n336\n00:25:35,847 --> 00:25:38,517\nThere are no families.\n\n337\n00:25:42,062 --> 00:25:45,732\nI see. So, um,\n\n338\n00:25:45,857 --> 00:25:49,778\nwhat about...\nsocietal structure?\n\n339\n00:25:49,903 --> 00:25:52,405\nGovernment.\nNo, there''s\nno need for one.\n\n340\n00:25:52,531 --> 00:25:56,576\n- You have no laws?\n- No laws. No lawyers.\n\n341\n00:25:56,701 --> 00:25:59,412\nHow do you know\nright from wrong?\n\n342\n00:25:59,538 --> 00:26:03,291\nEvery being\nin the universe knows\nright from wrong, Mark.\n\n343\n00:26:06,378 --> 00:26:09,297\nBut what if--\n\n344\n00:26:09,422 --> 00:26:12,842\nif someone did do\nsomething wrong--\n\n345\n00:26:12,926 --> 00:26:17,055\ncommitted murder or rape--\n\n346\n00:26:17,180 --> 00:26:19,224\nhow would you punish them?\n\n347\n00:26:22,602 --> 00:26:25,021\nLet me tell you\nsomething, Mark.\n\n348\n00:26:25,105 --> 00:26:27,732\nYou humans, most of you,\n\n349\n00:26:27,816 --> 00:26:30,569\nsubscribe to this policy\nof "an eye for an eye,\n\n350\n00:26:30,652 --> 00:26:33,071\na life for a life,"\nwhich is known\nthroughout the universe...\n\n351\n00:26:33,154 --> 00:26:35,073\nfor its stupidity.\n\n352\n00:26:35,156 --> 00:26:37,701\nEven your Buddha and your Christ\nhad quite a different vision,\n\n353\n00:26:37,784 --> 00:26:41,538\nbut nobody''s paid much attention\nto them, not even the Buddhists\nor the Christians.\n\n354\n00:26:43,164 --> 00:26:46,751\n[ Sighs ]\nYou humans,\n\n355\n00:26:46,876 --> 00:26:50,297\nsometimes it''s hard to imagine\nhow you''ve made it this far.\n\n356\n00:26:52,632 --> 00:26:54,509\n[Swing Creaking]\n\n357\n00:27:01,182 --> 00:27:03,768\n[Dr. Powel l]\nJosh, be careful.\n\n358\n00:27:05,228 --> 00:27:07,314\n[Rachel]\nOkay, kids. Let''s go.\nThe hot dogs are ready.\n\n359\n00:27:07,439 --> 00:27:10,108\n[Playful Chattering]\n\n360\n00:27:11,359 --> 00:27:14,154\nHey. Where were